headline: Honeywell upgraded at JPM as breakup nears and aerospace momentum builds
summary: Investing.com -- JPMorgan upgraded Honeywell to Overweight, saying the stock’s discount to its sum-of-the-parts valuation and improving underlying momentum create an opportunity ahead of the planned breakup.
